name: See-Threepio
Lore: 'C-3PO was Jabba''s ''khan chita,'' or translator. Survived more battles than most members of the Alliance. Wasn''t informed of R2-D2''s role in the rescue of Han.',
Text: 'Deploys only to a Jabba''s Palace site. Once per game, when replacing another C-3PO, retrieve 3 Force. When in battle with your other droid and a Rebel, adds one battle destiny. R2-D2 deploys and moves for free to same location.',
